<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Projet partie 1 : Authentification</title>
	<link href="/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="screen" />
	<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
</head>
<body>

	<h1>Service d'authenfication</h1>
	
	<p>Bonjour, vous n'êtes pas connecté.<br />
	Pour profiter de ce service merci de vous connecter si vous possédez un compte, de vous inscrire dans le cas contraire.</p>
	
	<div id="connexion">
		<h2>Connexion</h2>
		
		<form method="post" action="">
			<div class="field">
				<label for="label_login">Identifiant :</label>
				<input type="text" name="login" id="label_login" placeholder="Login" required />
			</div>
			<div class="field">
				<label for="label_password">Mot de passe :</label>
				<input type="password" name="password" id="label_password" placeholder="Password" required />
			</div>
			<div class="field_button">
				<input type="submit" value="Se connecter" />
			</div>
		</form>
	</div>
	
	<div id="inscription">
		<h2>Inscription</h2>
		
		<form method="post" action="">
			<div class="field">
				<label for="label_login">Identifiant :</label>
				<input type="text" name="login" id="label_login" placeholder="Login" required />
			</div>
			<div class="field">
				<label for="label_password">Mot de passe :</label>
				<input type="password" name="password" id="label_password" placeholder="Password" required />
			</div>
			<div class="field_button">
				<input type="submit" value="S'inscrire" />
			</div>
		</form>
	</div>
	
	<div class="clear"></div>
	
</body>
</html>
